Timberwolves CAD Release 2025

FRC Team 1153 is proud to present our 2025 robot: Lagotto!

  • Onshape
  • Code
    Assembly 1(1)2547×3296 3.12 MB

Featuring a 1 stage elevator with L1, L2, L3, and algae into the processor and barge, a ground algae intake, and a sub-15 second deep climb, this was one of our most successful seasons yet!

Captaining every event in our district, finalist at district championships, and finalist in the Hopper Division! Additionally, we won three distinct technical awards: Industrial Design, Excellence in Engineering, and our first Autonomous Award, and had two Dean’s List Finalists at the World Championships for the first time! (We joined the hexfecta this year!)

We would like to thank all of our alliance partners for making our season so successful.

We are proud to have built one of our strongest and most unique robots in our team’s history, and add another two silvers to our long, gold free history!
